<C>__{chris}
<D>__{what is that? the slabs?}
<C>__{rainey}
<D>__{it's down in niland, california. you know where the salton sea is?}
<C>__{chris}
<D>__{near san diego, yeah?}
<C>__{rainey}
<D>__{well about 200 miles northeast of there, but yeah. niland's off the east shore of salton. wild place. the navy bulldozed and abandoned a base there. all that's left is a grid of concrete foundations. they're scattered over about a square mile or so.}
